<paragraph blockId="0.[1250,2129,901,1009]" pageId="0" pageNumber="52">• Medium-sized arboreal marsupials with strong facial markings and one or more distinct dorsal stripes. • 30-80 cm.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1250,2130,1256,1482]" box="[1250,1597,1256,1285]" pageId="0" pageNumber="52">• Australasian Region.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1250,2130,1256,1482]" pageId="0" pageNumber="52">• Montane forest, lowland forest, and sclerophyll forest and woodland, some species in rainforest.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1250,2130,1256,1482]" box="[1250,1723,1366,1404]" pageId="0" pageNumber="52">• 3 genera, 12 species, 18 taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1250,2130,1256,1482]" pageId="0" pageNumber="52">• | species Critically Endangered, 3 species Endangered; no species Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
